00:03:00.560 --> 00:03:04.219
The double-breasted kind of lost its place
in World War II.

00:03:04.219 --> 00:03:07.620
It was just something that a lot of men stopped
wearing when they came back from the war.

00:03:07.620 --> 00:03:12.889
In addition, it used more fabric, so a lot
of factories stopped using it because of rationing.

00:03:12.889 --> 00:03:19.329
But before World War II, there was a time
that the double breasted was purchased and

00:03:19.329 --> 00:03:23.510
worn as much as the single-breasted, but the
double-breasted was considered more formal.

00:03:23.510 --> 00:03:27.659
So how could you take a single-breasted suit,
which like this that has the deep V, and a

00:03:27.659 --> 00:03:32.260
double-breasted usually that buttons up like
this -- that small distinction actually made

00:03:32.260 --> 00:03:36.139
the double breasted appear to be more formal,
more buttoned up.

00:03:36.139 --> 00:03:40.799
So how you could you take a single-breasted
suit and get more miles out of it and make

00:03:40.799 --> 00:03:42.809
it appear to be more buttoned up?

00:03:42.809 --> 00:03:46.599
You put it on the same level as the double-breasted.

00:03:46.599 --> 00:03:47.870
Introduce the vest.

00:03:47.870 --> 00:03:53.449
Now, the vest or waistcoat, whatever you want
to call it, it was originally used by messengers

00:03:53.449 --> 00:03:54.449
who rode horses.

00:03:54.449 --> 00:03:59.439
It was something that you're outside all day
riding on a horse in the wind, in the weather,

00:03:59.439 --> 00:04:02.900
and you need extra layers, so vests were developed.

00:04:02.900 --> 00:04:05.790
They initially started off as big pieces of
cloth.

00:04:05.790 --> 00:04:11.099
They eventually became their own type of garment,
but it was meant to be worn under a jacket

00:04:11.099 --> 00:04:13.220
and to add warmth.

00:04:13.220 --> 00:04:18.080
It eventually made its way into formal wear
after enough use in multiple wars.

00:04:18.080 --> 00:04:19.310
Men began to like it.

00:04:19.310 --> 00:04:21.049
They find that they could contrast the colors.

00:04:21.049 --> 00:04:25.500
