having them to go out and purchase an entire

00:04:25.500 --> 00:04:27.220
new suit.

00:04:27.220 --> 00:04:29.760
Jackets were really expensive; vests, less
expensive.

00:04:29.760 --> 00:04:35.540
You saw that by wearing a similar colored
vest, you could actually get the same buttoned

00:04:35.540 --> 00:04:38.100
up look as the double breasted suit.

